{"tid":1468234,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全部唔準再講個輸字！心理小教室之自我實現預言self fulfilling prophecy","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:08:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:26:48.000Z","uid":251458,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1b4d69f7272288d4f9acdd5f8676ee6f18d13494","tid":1468234,"uid":251458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:08:43.000Z","msg":"大家好，老尾sir今日要講下Self-fulfilling prophecy, 中文叫<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自我實現預言[/</span>size=4]。<br />\n<br />\n呢個係一個[size=4]社會心理學</span>現象，是指人們<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">先入為主</span></span>的判斷，無論其正確與否，都將或多或少的影響到人們的<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">行為</span></span></span>，以至於這個判斷最後真的實現。通俗的說，自證預言就是我們總會在不經意間使我們自己的預言成為現實。<br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">信念同行為會互為影響</span></span>。如果你覺得身邊既人唔鐘意同自己玩，現實好大可能都會係咁樣。因為你既信念會不知不覺影響到你的行為，例如你會對身邊既人唔笑、表現無咁友善，最後令到其他人真係唔想同你玩。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">要記住，你意識層面的想法並不是真正影響事情的原因，你潛意識裡固有的信念才是主導事情發展的力量所在！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n再比多一個大腦科學/心理學知識大家。<br />\n到底笑令你覺得開心定你開心先會笑？<br />\n答案係兩個都岩！人的大腦其實沒那麼聰明，或者咁講，易收錯signal.<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同埋因為保護自己，人的大腦傾向易記住負面東西，令你避免身處危險中！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實你係絕對有能力意志控制你的大腦與行為！但當人不停講輸輸輸，見到個輸字就唔方唔輸。<br />\n(你仲記得你細個個藍絲老豆賭馬叫你唔係輸輸聲嗎？)<br />\n就係因為呢d字眼絕對影響心理，繼而影響信念，最後影響行為。<br />\n<br />\n你可以嘗試了解正向心理學，<br />\n學習以正面方式鼓勵自己。<br />\n希望連登仔開post唔好話&quot;今晚輸撚到仆街&quot;, <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">試下講&quot;我地今晚嬴得唔夠精彩同漂亮，要改進&quot;.</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日講住咁多，推得上去既<br />\n下次教和理非點樣用<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">行為心理學</span></span>同勇武溝通。唔好令勇武覺得我地割蓆"},{"pid":"31f41bc533786d3179f001be90b3f6021187244a","tid":1468234,"uid":251458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:08:56.000Z","msg":"十連推"},{"pid":"7dc11a941a0c1b09764937c652f5561b32891a6a","tid":1468234,"uid":251458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:09:06.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"e3c8abb2fe44caab195d58e9293fe287083d032a","tid":1468234,"uid":251458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:09:16.000Z","msg":"3333推"},{"pid":"0cc8762461bb2e8239c6bdd04f73736c285754cf","tid":1468234,"uid":251458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:09:28.000Z","msg":"444444推"},{"pid":"a0204aaa4bd9b86bbbb367da81a00d0646817439","tid":1468234,"uid":251458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:09:41.000Z","msg":"5.嬴得唔夠靚"},{"pid":"9be6468ae88fd6ed1a0759c0981fff643d0a8311","tid":1468234,"uid":251458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:09:53.000Z","msg":"6.嬴得唔夠靚"},{"pid":"873bcf817e9973db7cd56d61143878e955338d8c","tid":1468234,"uid":251458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:10:05.000Z","msg":"7.嬴得唔夠靚"},{"pid":"3d4192ad554e78792c75e8590268e8a63139e665","tid":1468234,"uid":251458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:10:19.000Z","msg":"8.嬴得唔夠靚"},{"pid":"db6bc98d49465765d79b1e481dffdc68ceb7d6d8","tid":1468234,"uid":251458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:10:29.000Z","msg":"99999/10"},{"pid":"cca1f9b192bebf40ab0fe7825f0d2a4e1377b5db","tid":1468234,"uid":251458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:10:44.000Z","msg":"十連 ..........."},{"pid":"6111b10680b32622c88703b3a29bf43959c4186b","tid":1468234,"uid":251458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"